# TarotAI Scripts

This directory contains various utility scripts for managing the TarotAI project.

## Directory Structure

- `setup/`: Scripts for initial setup and dependency management
- `processing/`: Scripts for data processing and generation
- `maintenance/`: Scripts for code maintenance and cleanup

## Usage

### Setup
```bash
# Run full setup
./setup.sh

# Install dependencies only
scripts/setup/install_dependencies.sh
```

### Processing
```bash
# Generate card meanings
scripts/processing/generate_meanings.sh

# Process Golden Dawn PDF
scripts/processing/process_pdf.sh
```

### Maintenance
```bash
# Clean up project
scripts/maintenance/clean.sh

# Format and lint code
scripts/maintenance/format.sh
```

## Voice Interface

The voice interface allows hands-free interaction:

```bash
# Start voice interface
tarotai voice

# Configure voice settings
tarotai voice --config
```

## Best Practices

1. Always run scripts from the project root directory
2. Use the provided scripts rather than running commands directly
3. Check script outputs for any warnings or errors
4. Commit changes after running processing scripts
